1282
01:31:25,939 --> 01:31:28,400
Stephen, when you get through
showing them to their rooms,

1283
01:31:28,483 --> 01:31:31,361
go fetch Hildi, get her cleaned up
and smelling real nice,

1284
01:31:31,444 --> 01:31:34,823
