1302
01:32:26,458 --> 01:32:28,334
Because I said so, that's why.

1303
01:32:28,460 --> 01:32:31,588
Dr. Schultz is my guest.
Hildi is my nigger.

1304
01:32:31,671 --> 01:32:34,841
