I make her available to him.

1305
01:32:34,924 --> 01:32:38,094
-But Monsieur Candie, she run off.
-Jesus Christ, Stephen.

1306
01:32:38,178 --> 01:32:40,889
What is the point of having a nigger
that speaks German

