beyond words.

1315
01:33:03,203 --> 01:33:05,663
It is time for me to rest my tired eyes.

1316
01:33:08,625 --> 01:33:09,876
[clicking tongue]

1317
01:33:10,877 --> 01:33:13,546
Y'all done heard the man!
Get her ass up out of there!

1318
01:33:13,963 --> 01:33:15,590
Cora, come here.

1319
01:33:16,591 --> 01:33:19,844
Get over there, get her cleaned up,
bring her back over here to Dr....

