01:36:24,904 --> 01:36:28,116
Dr. Schultz.
May I introduce to you Broomhilda?

1334
01:36:32,495 --> 01:36:34,289
Hildi, this is Dr. Schultz.

1335
01:36:36,374 --> 01:36:38,251
