1362
01:40:40,451 --> 01:40:41,452
[gasps]

1363
01:40:44,705 --> 01:40:45,873
[sighs]

1364
01:40:49,252 --> 01:40:51,712
You silver-tongued devil, you.

1365
01:40:53,548 --> 01:40:55,258
-Hurry up, girl.
-These ready, Miss Cora.

1366
01:40:55,341 --> 01:40:56,842
No, no, no. They drinking, tonight.

1367
01:40:56,926 --> 01:40:59,679
Go downstairs, get the big jug
with the red stuff Monsieur Candie like.

1368
01:40:59,762 --> 01:41:02,848
Get your pretty ass out the way. You know
you like it.

1369
01:41:02,974 --> 01:41:05,726
