and I can see why.

1384
01:41:45,099 --> 01:41:46,392
He's a champion.

1385
01:41:46,475 --> 01:41:49,645
Mm-mm-mm. All three are champions.

1386
01:41:50,813 --> 01:41:51,856
Samson's the champion.

1387
01:41:53,065 --> 01:41:54,150
Them other two pretty good.

1388
01:41:56,152 --> 01:41:58,946
-Calvin, what's this nigger you let--?
-It's all right, it's all right.

1389
01:41:59,030 --> 01:42:00,823
